Usage from the command line </title>

<p><app>Font Manager</app> can be invoked from the Command line to perform the following basic tasks:</p> 

<list>
<item><p>-i install font files</p></item>
<item><p>-e enable a font family</p></item>
<item><p>-d disable a font family</p></item>
<item><p>--list list font families</p></item>
<item><p>--list-full list font families and all faces (JSON output)</p></item>
<item><p>-V verbose (debugging mode, undocumented)</p></item>
</list>


<p>See the <code>font-manager(1)</code> man page for details. </p>


